description: A Russian army medical team sent to Italy in March to help fight the pandemic is heading home.
title: Coronavirus: Russia brings army doctors home from Italy
title_page: Coronavirus: Russia brings army doctors home from Italy - BBC News
maintext: But it is unclear how effective the mission was. Russia's military said its field hospital had taken in 93 patients and 62 of them had recovered and been discharged. Other personnel were filmed disinfecting buildings in the area.
